Class OModelCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.OModelCreator

    OModelBuilder, OModelCopier

    public abstract class OModelCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for creating an OModel object representing either a set of ontologies loaded directly from disk, or the contents of an existing model.
